OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, a fine
OL,6,Fbut windy day is expected, and widely
OL,7,Fsunny with only limited amounts of
OL,8,Fhigh cloud. Warm, especially out the
OL,9,Fwind, but cooler in any onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely clear skies overnight
OL,12,Fwill allow for temperatures to fall.
OL,13,FWith winds easing, the odd patch of
OL,14,Ffrost cannot be ruled out and very
OL,15,Fisolated valley fog is possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day,
OL,18,Fwith only limited amounts of high
OL,19,Fcloud. With lighter winds and widely
OL,20,Fsunny skies, it will be feeling warmer
OL,21,Fthan on Tuesday for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
