OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCooler Thursday and Friday, and
OL,7,Flargely dry with variable cloud and
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Some overnight frost
OL,9,Fpossible, and winds strengthening
OL,10,Flater Friday. Further rain spreading
OL,11,Feast Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
